{
  "texts": [
    "For example, Grammarly is a popular tool that uses NLP to identify and correct grammatical errors in written work (Grammarly, 2020).",
    "Similarly, Turnitin is a plagiarism detection tool that uses NLP to compare student writing against a large database of existing work to identify any instances of plagiarism (Turnitin, n.d.).",
    "AI-powered writing tools like Grammarly, and Turnitin are being widely used by students and academics to check their writing for errors, plagiarism, and grammatical mistakes (Yan, 2023).",
    "Technological advances in artificial intelligence (AI) have been rapidly progressing over the past few years and are becoming increasingly prevalent in academic writing (Alkaissi & McFarlane, 2023).",
    "AI can help researchers write academic papers more efficiently and effectively than ever before."
  ]
}